APPENDIX

Definitions

1I "Anti-corruption Guidelines" means, for purposes of paragraph 5 of the Appendix to the
General Conditions, the Bank's "Guidelines on Preventing and Combating Fraud and
Corruption in Program-for-Results Financing," dated February 1, 2012, and revised July
10, 2015.

2. "Category" means a category set forth in the table in Section IV.A.2 of Schedule 2 to this
Agreement.

3. "DLMH" means the Program Implementing Entity's Directorate of Indian Medicine and
Homeopathy, or any successor thereto.

4. "Disbursement Linked Indicator" or "DLI" means each of the disbursement linked
indicators listed in the first column of the matrix set forth in Schedule 3 to this Agreement.

5. "Disbursement Linked Result" or "DLR" means in respect of a given DLI, the result under
said DLI as set forth in the matrix in Schedule 3 to this Agreement, on the basis of the
achievement of which, the amount of the Loan allocated to said result may be withdrawn
in accordance with the provisions of Section IV of Schedule 2 to this Agreement.

6. "DME" means the Program Implementing Entity's Directorate of Medical Education, or
any successor thereto.

7. "DMRHS" means the Program Implementing Entity's Directorate of Medical and Rural
Health Services, or any successor thereto.

8. "DoF" means Tamil Nadu's Department of Finance, or any successor thereto.

9. "DoHFW" means Tamil Nadu's Department of Health and Family Welfare, or any
successor thereto.

10. "DPH" means the Program Implementing Entity's Directorate of Public Health, or any
successor thereto.

I1. "Empowered Committee" or "EC" means the committee referred to in Section I.B. 1(b) of
the Schedule to the Program Agreement.

12. "ESSA" means the Environmental and Social Systems Assessment, disclosed on
November 19, 2018 setting forth the description of the Program's activities, assessing the
Borrower's and Program Implementing Entity's environmental and social management
systems, detailing the Program's environmental and social benefits, risks and impacts, and
recommending remedial measures to strengthen the social and environmental systems
performance.
13. "Fiscal Year" or "FY" means the Borrower's fiscal year, which begins on April I of each
calendar year and ends of March 31 of the next calendar year.

14. "General Conditions" means the "International Bank for Reconstruction and Development
General Conditions for IBRD Financing, Program-for-Results Financing", dated July 14,
2017.

15. "Group A Facility" means an advanced trauma center that provides a wide set of surgeries
including general, orthopedic, plastic. vascular and neuro surgeries.

16. "Group B Facility" means a basic trauma center that provides a limited set of surgeries
including general and orthopedic surgeries.

17. "Health Facilities" collectively refers to Primary Care Facilities, Secondary Care Facilities
and Tertiary Care Facilities.

18 "HMIS" means the Program Implementing Entity's health management information
system.

19. Independent Verification Agent" or "IVA" means the agent appointed, or to be appointed,
by the Program Implementing Entity for the purpose of verifying achievement of DLRs in
accordance with Section I.D of the Schedule to the Program Agreement.

20. "NABH" means the Borrower's National Accreditation Board for Hospitals & Healthcare
Providers, or its successor thereto.

21. "NCD" means non-communicable disease, and includes hypertension, diabetes, cervical
cancer, breast cancer, oral cancer and mental health related disease.

22. "NHM" means the Program Implementing Entity's National Health Mission, or any
successor thereto.

23. "NQAS" means the National Quality Assurance Standards developed by the Borrower's
Ministry of Health and Family Welfare to assess and provide quality certification to public
health facilities.

24. "Primary Care Facility" means a health facility where health professionals act as a first
point of consultation for all patients, including Primary Health Centers and community
health centers.

25. "Primary Health Centers" means a health facility designated as a PHC by Tamil Nadu.

26. "Priority District(s)" means any of the Program Implementing Entity's districts of Ariyalur,
Dharmapuri, Ramanathapuram. The Nilgris, Theni, Thoothukkudi, Tirunelveli,
Tiruvannamalai and Virudhunagar, as such list may be modified with prior concurrence of
the Bank.
27 "Program Action Plan" means the Borrower's plan dated February 5. 2019 and referred to
in Section I.B of Schedule 2 to this Agreement, as may be amended from time to time with
the agreement of the Bank.

28. "Program Implementing Entity" means the Borrower's state of Tarmil Nadu.

29. "Program Management Unit" or "PMU"' means the unit referred to in Section I.B. 1(a) of
the Schedule to the Program Agreement.

30. "Program Steering Committee" or "PSC" means the committee referred to in Section
LB. 1(c) of the Schedule to the Program Agreement.

31. "Secondary Care Facility" means a health facility providing acute care or necessary
treatment for a short period of time for a brief but serious illness, injury, or other health
condition, including district headquarter, taluk and non-taluk hospitals.

32. "Signature Date" means the later of the two dates on which the Borrower and the Bank
signed this Agreement and such definition applies to all references to "the date of the Loan
Agreement" in the General Conditions.

33. "STEPS Survey" means a survey using the stepwise approach to surveillance methodology
developed by the World Health Organization to enable Tamil Nadu to develop its own
surveillance system to monitor and fight against NCDs.

34. "Tamil Nadu" means the Borrower's state of Tamil Nadu.

35. "Tertiary Care Facility" means a specialized consultative health care facility, usually for
inpatients and on referral from a Primary Care Facility or Secondary Care Facility,
including a medical college.

36. "TNFSDA" means the Program Implementing Entity's Tamil Nadu Food Safety and Drug
Administration, or any successor thereto.

37. "TNHSP Society" means the Program Implementing Entity's Tamil Nadu Health Systems
Project Society, or any successor thereto.

38. "TNMSC" means the Program Implementing Entity's Tamil Nadu Medical Services
Corporation, or any successor thereto.